{"tid":905780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"種族屠殺罪成　兩赤柬領袖囚終身","createTime":"2018-11-17T12:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T16:30:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05b2df53cd6d802bdb994ce4b143251e4cb64d26","tid":905780,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548054&d=%2FffIv5uq8TfcL3mG%2FY4yqNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2562d2f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548054&h=fce3fe3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548054</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月17日 <br />\n<br />\n種族屠殺罪成　兩赤柬領袖囚終身<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181117/large/a1104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181117%2Flarge%2Fa1104a.gif&h=7a4baadf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨兩名前赤柬領袖昨日被判干犯種族屠殺罪成，判囚終身，是赤柬政權倒下近40年來首次有赤柬領袖因種族屠殺受審及被定罪判刑。92歲的赤柬第二號領導人農謝（Nuon Chea）和87歲的赤柬前總理喬森潘（Khieu Samphan）於2014年已被裁定干犯人道罪行，判處終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n判詞指赤柬政權對越南人和占族進行種族屠殺，占族平民被大規模殺害，數以百計的越南平民和士兵在S-21審訊中心被施酷刑及處決。法官指雖無證據顯示喬森潘有份屠殺占族，但他身為聯合指揮官仍需對屠殺越南人負責；而農謝與前赤柬總書記波爾布特（Pol Pot）擁最終決策權，故需為屠殺越南人和占族負責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致全國1/4人死亡<br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨法院特別法庭（ECCC）於2006年由聯合國支持成立，用以審判赤柬領袖，目前只得三人被定罪。柬埔寨於1975至79年間淪為赤柬暴政下的「殺戮戰場」，約200萬人死於大屠殺、饑荒、奴役和酷刑，佔全國人口約1/4。殺人狂魔波爾布特早於1998年去世，未有面臨審判。同是前赤柬骨幹的現任首相洪森（Hun Sen）稱為免引起局勢動盪，不容許再開展更多調查。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/法新社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n法官判CNN記者暫可返白宮採訪<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n英同志畫家名作　破紀錄七億成交"},{"pid":"209f65007005225e14cbecbb6c49aed25ab2fa82","tid":905780,"uid":161341,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"與此同時<br />\n支共：毛仔萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd84c571942471768fd40ab28971865244006823","tid":905780,"uid":104425,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"聯合國呢d臭閪組織真係冇撚用<br />\n柬埔寨就幫人成立特別法庭<br />\n眾志交意見書就delete人<br />\n仲話尊重領土主權<br />\n偽善到極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb51901ea8ba799b6a3e87fb72f3057441c0dc18","tid":905780,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"一個92歲另一個87歲 <br />\n<br />\n判終身監禁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dda19a6a93f985ab0eec7fc6f6f1f0c7e91e38b","tid":905780,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd84c571942471768fd40ab28971865244006823","tid":905780,"uid":104425,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"聯合國呢d臭閪組織真係冇撚用<br />\n柬埔寨就幫人成立特別法庭<br />\n眾志交意見書就delete人<br />\n仲話尊重領土主權<br />\n偽善到極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"擺明兩條失勢廢老冇錢醫病<br />\n囚終身用政府錢幫佢醫<br />\n醫好先保外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de6599809a39d2c7ff08559fbc679caf630297d","tid":905780,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"殺左成個國家1/4人"},{"pid":"2e31fefe2433603c2dbe788de21da03b997b2ab4","tid":905780,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"成90歲人先終身 做下樣就算"},{"pid":"dc5998e0270131585a4554da48caa36bed84f85a","tid":905780,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T14:59:48.0